reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The cables arrived quickly and were in good working order. I have used one for two days, and so far so good. This is in reference to the 3-star ratings I gave for durability and sturdiness. I can't give an intelligent rating after two days. They do not feel cheaply made. Time will tell about their ability to last long. I do believe they are an excellent value- 6 cords for less than the price of 1 in a retail store.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Reliable and Fast Charging
reviews.reviewText: Apple MFi Certified (5/5):The cables are Apple MFi certified, ensuring they meet Apple's strict standards for quality and compatibility. You can trust that they will work seamlessly with your Apple devices.Multiple Lengths (4/5):The pack includes cables of different lengths, ranging from 3 to 10 feet. This variety allows you to choose the most suitable cable length for your charging and syncing needs.Fast Charging (4/5):These cables support fast charging, allowing you to charge your Apple devices quickly and efficiently.Data Transfer (4/5):In addition to charging, the cables also support data transfer, making it easy to sync your devices with your computer.Durability (4/5):The cables are built to be durable and long-lasting, reducing the risk of wear and tear over time.Convenient Multipack (4/5):Having multiple cables in one pack is convenient, especially for households with multiple Apple devices or for individuals who need spare cables for various locations.Compatibility (5/5):These cables are compatible with a wide range of Apple devices, including iPhones, iPads, and iPods, making them versatile for different Apple users.Affordable (4/5):Considering you get a pack of six cables, the price is reasonable and provides good value.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value in a multi-pack, durable cables
reviews.reviewText: I bought this multi-pack of cables to replace the standard/original issued Apple cables that come with the iPhone and iPad as over time the original cables have frayed (specifically the point where the cable and lightning connector meet).The multi-pack was a superb value as it includes 6 total cables. I really like the variety of lengths included as they work well for different locations around the house, at my office, or in my car. The cables are durable and covered in a flexible fabric-like outer material - so much better than regular plastic. I would definitely buy these again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good Value - 4/5 Durability
reviews.reviewText: I have bought these charger packs with the different lengths a handful of times, I usually get 5-6+ months out of the chargers. It's perfect for you if you want to leave a charger in different places. Personally I use one for my bed, one for my car, and one for a power bank so I'm not losing them. Good replacement overall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are my very favorite charging cords! I’ve bought 2 sets so far and they last for awhile. I’ll be ordering more soon as I use them for everything like car, house and outside uses! Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for the price
reviews.reviewText: They don’t last super long but it’s a good deal for the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Works great, feels solid and charges fast. Great value if youre looking for more lightning cables.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Something not quite right
reviews.reviewText: These do OK for charging, but I think the wire is super thin and connectors are low quality. My iPad takes double the amount of time to charge, and sometimes stops halfway through. My phone keeps disconnecting from the car when I’m driving, and neither of these is an issue with other cables I’ve had in the past. As nice as the price is, I’m buying better cables before these wear out.
